glibc (2.3.5-1ubuntu11) breezy; urgency=low

  * Jeff Bailey <jbailey@ubuntu.com>

    * Make langpacks less heavy to use.
      - debian/patches/ubuntu-altlocaledir.dpatch: Update
        Thanks to Martin Pitt for this patch! (Ubuntu# 11344)

    * Make sure services using NSS are restarted.
      - debian/debhelper.in/libc.postinst: Set guard to 2.3.5-1
        (Ubuntu #13658)

    * Add Asturian locale from Spain
      - debian/patches/ast_ES.dpatch: New file
      - debian/patches/00list: Upate
        Thanks to Jordi Mallach for this locale!

    * Protect against macro expansion in __memset_1
      - debian/patches/ubuntu-12864.dpatch: New file
      - debian/patches/00list: Update
        Thanks to Matthias Klose for this patch! (Ubuntu #12864)

    * Avoid segfault in initstate_r
      - debian/patches/ubuntu-10245.dpatch: New file
      - debian/patches/00list: Update
      Thanks to Alex Mauer for reporting this! (Ubuntu #10245)

    * The French weekday starts on Monday.
      - debian/patches/fr_FR.dpatch: New File
      - debian/patches/00list: Update
      Thanks to Sebastien Bacher for reporting this! (Ubuntu #12794)

 -- Jeff Bailey <jbailey@ubuntu.com>  Thu,  1 Sep 2005 20:19:50 -0400

