  * debian/patches/pthread-sigsetjmp.dpatch: Fix __sigsetmask function
    declaration. Triggered by gcc-4.0.

 -- Matthias Klose <doko@ubuntu.com>  Tue,  1 Feb 2005 13:57:22 +0100

