  * The "Perl Sucks" release.
  * debian/libc.postinst: Steal updatercd shell function from sysvinit postinst.
    Use it for devpts.sh. (closes:Bug#45867,#45879,#45880,#45885,#45895)
    Bitch-slap perl maintainers. :)
